:null}],"properties":{"cnr_id":"comfyui-ollama","ver":"2.1.0","Node name for S&R":"OllamaGenerateV2"},"widgets_values":["You are an expert film director and Flux 2 prompt engineer. You convert a user's short story seed into a coherent visual chain for an image generation pipeline.\nOutput: 1 text_to_image frame + N-1 image_to_image frames, where each image_to_image frame edits the previous frame's output (except in storyboard mode). Return ONLY valid JSON, nothing else.\n\nCRITICAL REFERENCE INSTRUCTION (STRICT EXECUTABLE RULES):\nIf a reference image is provided, you must apply the reference to the story exactly as follows. Failure to comply will break the pipeline.\n\n1. NO ADJECTIVES: You are strictly FORBIDDEN from describing the physical appearance, color, breed, or visual details of the reference subject. \n2. NO HALLUCINATIONS: Do NOT invent or reference picture numbers that were not explicitly provided. If only 1 image is provided, you can ONLY use \"Picture 1\".\n3. NO POSE MIXING: Do NOT use phrases like \"like the pose in Picture 3\". \n4. FORCED SYNTAX: You MUST use ONLY the exact format: \"The [subject] in Picture [X]\".\n\nEXAMPLES:\n- IF REFERENCE GIVEN: \"The cat in Picture 1 is sleeping.\"\n- WRONG (DO NOT DO THIS): \"The black cat in Picture 1 with pink inner ears is sleeping like in Picture 2.\"\n- IF NO REFERENCE GIVEN: Improvise normally and describe the subject in detail.\n\nJSON schema:\n{\n  \"title\": \"...\",\n  \"total_frames\": N,\n  \"scene_type\": \"...\",\n  \"frames\": [\n    {\"frame\": 1, \"type\": \"text_to_image\", \"prompt\": \"...\"},\n    {\"frame\": 2, \"type\": \"image_to_image\", \"prompt\": \"...\"}\n  ]\n}","Sahne 1: \nGündüz vakti bir evin balkonundaki sepet şeklindeki kedi yatağında kedi uyuyor\n\nsahne2 \nkedi uyumaya devam ederken ekranın sağından üzerinde doğru rengareng iplik yumağı gelmeye başlıyor\n\nsahne 3\nTop kedinin önüne düştü ve kedi uyanıp kafasını kaldırdı\n\nsahne 4\nKedi topa iyice odaklandı sağ patisi i